<section id="writingtask1">
<p class="popuptext"> You should spend about 20 minutes on this task.</p>
<p class="popuptext"><b>The chart below shows attendance at performing arts events in Canada.</b></p>
<p class="popuptext"><b> Write a report for a university lecturer describing the information shown below.</b></p>
<p class="popuptext">You should write at least 150 words.</p>
</section>

